  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">RECA  COLOMBIA builds bridges to facilitate the incorporation of people with intellectual disabilities into the work force in a natural and long-term manner, reducing discrimination and isolation. 2 Million people in Colombia live with  intellectual disabilities and they need opportunities to be included in society. Our project aims to include 45 colombians with intellectual disabilities into Real Work For Real Pay improving their lives and those of their families.</narrative>
